{"tid":1887361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【推足11頁，都係得552個人打TVB戰線】今日洗版精選 - 仲食醫之選？塑化劑超標呀！(19 Feb)","createTime":"2020-02-19T13:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T01:54:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0bcb13a9e589a821588d690dbf4120d12df7ad7","tid":1887361,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"[轉載］<br />\n<br />\n平時幾位巴打好辛苦推足5-6頁，有500幾嬲我都好欣慰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係頂你個掣，尋晚打海狗丸推到11頁都係得500幾嬲，都唔成比例嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4rPji4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4rPji4.png&h=0662dad9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n不過如果戰力係去咗YouTube嗰邊，我都理解嘅，個個戰線都要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">To: 幫手推post手足，試下peak hour 推到第5頁就收工，反正點推都係500幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n <br />\n<strong>呢幾日去黃店食嘢，電視播呢條片，諗起有血有淚有人犠牲，我都唔知點解控制唔到眼淚</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好忘記，為咗香港搵一個啱自己嘅崗位繼續行落去<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Coyd9Lm6Yig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCoyd9Lm6Yig&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5PSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=b036d448\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Coyd9Lm6Yig</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【永久抵制精選@19 Feb 2020】</span></strong></span><br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.永久抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br /